_sText: dm_hokan is a deathmatch style Counter-Strike: Source map, with a large, open environment. There are lots of tunnels through which to navigate the map, and many crates and hiding places to surprise your enemies and play tactically. There are ramps that allow players to go on top of tunnels, and some gaps in the tops of the tunnels to better allow players to literally get the drop on their foes. dm_hokan is a map that demands you to be constantly thinking and checking your corners, because the enemy could come from anywhere...
